Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,### 前奏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.44,0:00:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(475,450)\blur1}看，月光洒下，在其中的同志
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.35,0:00:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)\blur1}我们什么东西都不用害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.14,0:00:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)\blur1}看，战争令下，在这样的时机
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.02,0:00:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,300)\blur1}我们什么退路都已经没有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.54,0:00:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,450)\blur1}对著这黑夜，对著这明月
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.19,0:00:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)\blur1}发誓你将会付出你所有拥有的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.42,0:00:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,850)\blur1}为永恒的黑夜，为无尽的黑夜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.75,0:00:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(330,850)\blur1}正是时候...
Comment: 0,0:00:54.44,0:00:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,### 导歌-1
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.45,0:01:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,900)\blur1}请为了你们未来，做好准备
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.84,0:01:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,150)\blur1}决下心，是否要和我一起战到命无
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.00,0:01:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,450)\blur1}挺起胸，气扬志高
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.27,0:01:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,900)\blur1}面对太阳，这就是我们的月之抗争
Comment: 0,0:01:17.64,0:01:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,### 副歌-1
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.65,0:01:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}往前进，拿下胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.80,0:01:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}与地上的月光一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.04,0:01:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}手抓紧，那份自由
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.15,0:01:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}即使得要交付性命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.34,0:01:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}往前进，拿下胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.47,0:01:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}与天上的星光一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.70,0:01:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}手抓紧，那份自由
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.84,0:01:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,900)\blur1}即使得要碎骨粉身
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.42,0:01:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,900)\blur1}我们必须向前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.84,0:01:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}才能够夺得胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.67,0:01:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,900)\blur1}伴随著，天空中，高挂的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.35,0:02:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,900)\blur1}那般烧灼你的命
Comment: 0,0:02:00.54,0:02:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,### 导歌-2
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.52,0:02:05.82,Daybreaker,,0,0,0,,{\fad(830,320)\blur1}挥舞著，火红一般的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.89,0:02:10.10,Daybreaker,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,350)\blur1}她缓缓地降落到这土地上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.19,0:02:16.42,Daybreaker,,0,0,0,,{\fad(380,350)\blur1}她，已没有，像以前般的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.44,0:02:20.30,Daybreaker,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,350)\blur1}她也已经听不见我的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.34,0:02:25.95,Daybreaker,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,450)\blur1}我们俩曾经许下的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.99,0:02:32.15,Daybreaker,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,410)\blur1}两人的共同时光，全部都与光线一并消逝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.19,0:02:37.90,Daybreaker,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,650)\blur1}而就是再怎样微小的梦想和愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.04,0:02:42.65,Daybreaker,,0,0,0,,{\fad(650,900)\blur1}也终究是，无法，再现
Comment: 0,0:02:42.92,0:02:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,### 副歌-2
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.92,0:02:44.92,Daybreaker,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}大家都，粉身碎骨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.09,0:02:47.77,Daybreaker,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}我的同伴们通通都
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.34,0:02:50.32,Daybreaker,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}渐渐地，被烧成灰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.44,0:02:53.44,Daybreaker,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}被地上的阳光包裹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.62,0:02:55.60,Daybreaker,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}大家都，粉身碎骨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.77,0:02:58.44,Daybreaker,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}我的同伴无人生还
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.00,0:03:01.00,Daybreaker,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}渐渐地，被烧成灰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.14,0:03:06.50,Daybreaker,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,900)\blur1}被天上的日光照耀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.72,0:03:12.15,Daybreaker,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,900)\blur1}那太阳逐渐升起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.15,0:03:14.80,Daybreaker,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}暗夜渐渐地消失
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.99,0:03:22.62,Daybreaker,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,900)\blur1}伴随著，天空中，坠落的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.65,0:03:25.59,Daybreaker,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,900)\blur1}现在只剩我一人
Comment: 0,0:03:28.59,0:03:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,### 对话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:33.47,Nightmare,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,300)\blur1}「Luna... Luna...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.49,0:03:36.94,Nightmare,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}请你听我说... Luna
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.50,0:03:40.77,Nightmare,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}我的声音，你听得见吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.34,0:03:44.50,Nightmare,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}现在，是时候使用我的力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.65,0:03:47.80,Nightmare,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}我说，你这次不成功不行，是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.69,0:03:51.92,Nightmare,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}全部交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.15,0:03:55.32,Nightmare,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}接受我，掌握我的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:03:57.75,Nightmare,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}觉醒你的真正潜能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:02.70,Nightmare,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}要消灭太阳，只有这个方法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.17,0:04:05.40,Nightmare,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}就只剩这一条路了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.42,0:04:08.04,Nightmare,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}放弃你旧的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.05,0:04:19.75,Nightmare,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,8000)\blur1}并接受『梦魇之月』，你的新名字...」
